   70:  If  *GB_StoryProgress  <  .Story:Ch7_DefeatedMonstar % 45
   80:  	Call  MakeNpcs  ( .False $NpcGroupList_80245D94 )
   94:  Else
   9C:  	Call  MakeNpcs  ( .False $NpcGroupList_80245DD0 )
